Interface G2Definition

All Known Subinterfaces:
ClassDefinition, ConnectionDefinition, Definition, MessageDefinition, ObjectDefinition
public interface G2Definition

Encapsulates the powers of all class definitions in G2, both user-defined and System-defined.
